author: werpu
msg: We now have replaced the old list based system with a first rough version of a registry / strategy based one which works
on filter lists. While we were clearing this up we also improved the scan time in the whitelist filters by
moving from a string based compare system to one based on index maps.
The exection time was reduced by 50% just by this measure (being run on a loop which looped over a scan on 1000 classes
